Major Bodies of Water in the City of St. Louis

A simple features data set containing polygons for the major bodies of water in the city.

data(stl_sf_hydro)

Format

A simple feature with 2 rows and 4 variables:

HYDROID

Census identification number

NAME

name of body of water

SQMETER

area covered by water, square meters

geometry

simple features geometry
